{
  "stem": "747.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The government-- the Hungarian government.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it started to be fascist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's-- got-- every day got stronger and stronger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a new restriction came that we didn't have before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took from government offices-- all the Jewish guys were let-- let out-- dismissed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then came to the schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were still had-- by that time, I was not in elementary school-- but the children had problems.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the anti-Semitic children, they heard from their parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or mainly the Youth-- everywhere the Youth started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was something new, something exciting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They wore a uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they felt very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Youth-- the Nazi sympathizers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Youth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually, it worked like everywhere-- the scum, the one who had nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had-- they felt that they are getting elevated with-- by the joining the Nazi party-- what they called the Nyilas in Hungary-- but it was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And instead of all black shirts, they wore a green shirts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very painful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For example, we had a woman-- a washer woman-- because everything was done in the house-- we had-- Auntie Julie, who came to our house for years and years to wash the monthly big wash day.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother was very kind to her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had no husband and had four children, and had one son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The son used to come into our house, and my mother always gave her a-- him a big slice of bread with something, and my brothers' outgrown clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that kid never had a decent haircut, because the mother had had no money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was really a half-orphan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He-- he was almost part of our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
